General.Name: Linius Technologies Ltd
General.Description: Linius Technologies Limited engages in the development of computer software. The company also offers Linius Video Services Platform, a suite of tools that enable clients to manage vast libraries of virtualized videos, and generate and deliver personalized video content. It provides solutions in the area of sports, education, business, and blockchain. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
